[0.019, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\r\u001b[9A\u001b[92m⏺\u001b[5C\u001b[39m \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file \u001b[37m(ctrl+o to expand)\u001b[39m    \r\u001b[1B                                   \r\u001b[1B\u001b[92m⏺\u001b[1C\u001b[39m\u001b[1mUpdate\u001b[22m(.agentpolicy/state/ledger.json)\r\u001b[1B \u001b[1C⎿  Added \u001b[1m18\u001b[22m lines     \u001b[1C              \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[2m 62 \u001b[7C\u001b[22m\u001b[34m\"description\"\u001b[39m:\u001b[1C\u001b[32m\"Implemented all web UI: API client with JWT aut\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m     \u001b[2m    \u001b[22m \u001b[32mh flow (memory-only tokens, auto-refresh), AuthProvider context, 10 s\u001b[39m \u001b[1C   \u001b[1C \r\u001b[1B   \u001b[2C\u001b[2m    \u001b[1C\u001b[22m\u001b[32mhadcn/ui components (button, input, card, badge, dialog, select, toas\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m     \u001b[2m    \u001b[22m \u001b[32mt, table, label, tabs), 3 form components (login, appointment booking\u001b[39m       \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B   \u001b[2m    \u001b[22m \u001b[32m, patient intake), 5 data display components (stats card, appointment\u001b[39m\r\r\n\u001b[5C\u001b[2m \u001b[4C\u001b[22m\u001b[32m card,\u001b[1Cpatient\u001b[1Csummary,\u001b[1Cvisit\u001b[1Cnote,\u001b[1Cbilling\u001b[1Crow),\u001b[1Call\u001b[1C8\u001b[1Cpages\u001b[1C(login,\u001b[39m\r\r\n\u001b[5C\u001b[2m \u001b[4C\u001b[22m\u001b[32m dashboard\u001b[1Cwith\u001b[1Crole-specific\u001b[1Cviews,\u001b[1Cappointments\u001b[1Cwi"]
